description:

title: Listen To Internet Radio With Emacs And Eradio
description:
'eradio' is a simple Internet radio player for Emacs.  Installation and setup is super easy, since 'eradio' consists of only three functions (play, stop, toggle) and three variables that you may or may not need to edit.

REFERENCED:
► https://github.com/olavfosse/eradio
